# Applies only to `docker build -f examples/echo/Dockerfile` (BuildKit
# convention: a <dockerfile>.dockerignore next to the referenced Dockerfile
# takes precedence over a root .dockerignore). Keeps the build context lean
# and avoids shadowing the stub packages this build regenerates itself via
# `buf generate` in its "proto" stage.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
build/
dist/
tests/
src/signet/
src/admin/
examples/getsecret/
examples/restart_on_change/
